text: William Tackaert (born 9 August 1956) is a former Belgian racing cyclist. He rode in five editions of the Tour de France between 1979 and 1983. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian male cyclists Category:People from Zele Category:Tour de France cyclists Category:Sportspeople from East Flanders
